    "1 * 1 convolution can also be seen as fully connected, but it preserves the spatial structure of the feature layer and has better retention for features.",
    "We believe that the attention is superior when used superimposed, and the results of NetVLAD based on the attention may be better if the backbone network is replaced with the attention, which is not the focus of this paper.",
